SQL> SELECT p.country_name, f.year, AVG(hdi)
  2  FROM COUNTRIES p, FACTS f WHERE p.id_country = f.id_country AND f.hdi IS NOT NULL
  3  GROUP BY CUBE(p.country_name,f.year);

5795 lignes slectionnes.

SQL> SELECT p.country_name, f.year, AVG(hdi)
  2  FROM COUNTRIES p, FACTS f
  3  WHERE p.id_country = f.id_country AND f.hdi IS NOT NULL
  4  GROUP BY GROUPING SETS((p.country_name),(p.country_name, f.year))
  5  ORDER BY p.country_name, f.year;
